	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have an auto pormento thing in NT2, and I set the value to $0A, and I turn the pormento up thing on, and yeah it works fine. When I save and quit, and come back later, the value of the permento is $8A, and the auto pormento thing is off. What causes this? has anyone else had this problem? and this happens every single time I save/quite/come back. Pretty retarded bug, huh?  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_confused.gif" alt=":?" title="Confused" />

		

